- Liberty vs. Oppression: Green (#10B981, #D1FAE5)
- Authority vs. Subversion: Purple (#8B5CF6, #EDE9FE)
- Loyalty vs. Betrayal: Teal (#14B8A6, #CCFBF1)
- Purity vs. Degradation: Gold (#F59E0B, #FEF3C7)

**Icons:**
- Care/Harm: Heart
- Fairness/Cheating: Scale
- Liberty/Oppression: Shield
- Authority/Subversion: Crown
- Loyalty/Betrayal: Users linked
- Purity/Degradation: Sparkles

**Typography:**
- Conflict names: Bold, 18px
- Descriptions: Regular, 14px
- Questions: Medium, 15px
- Examples: Italic, 13px

