13.4 Testing Strategy
Unit Tests:

Conflict selection logic
Complexity validation
Character position calculations
Archetype-moral mappings
Data structure validation

Integration Tests:

Archetype Builder integration
Scene moral stakes
Map visualization
AI analysis flow
Database operations

E2E Tests:

Select moral conflict
Choose complexity
Define positions
Create character alignment
Use mapping tool
Request AI analysis
Apply suggestions
Navigate between views

Content Testing:

All 6 conflicts clear and accurate
Examples culturally appropriate
Questions guide effectively
AI suggestions relevant
No biased language

13.5 Analytics
javascript// Conflict Selection
trackEvent('moral_conflict_selected', {
  conflict_primary: conflictId,
  conflict_secondary: secondaryId || null,
  story_type: storyType,
  mode: userMode
});

// Complexity Selection
trackEvent('moral_complexity_chosen', {
  complexity: 'simple' | 'two_rights' | 'lesser_evil',
  conflict: conflictId
});

// Character Alignment
trackEvent('character_alignment_created', {
  character_archetype: archetype,
  starting_position: position,
  values_selected: valuesArray
});

// AI Analysis
trackEvent('moral_ai_analysis', {
  conflicts_detected: detectedCount,
  suggestions_count: suggestionCount
});

trackEvent('moral_suggestion_applied', {
  suggestion_type: type,
  conflict: conflictId
});

// Mapping Tool
trackEvent('moral_mapping_used', {
  characters_mapped: count,
  decision_points: count
});
